Quest:Across the Universe

From Wizard101 Wiki
Jump to: navigation, search

Quest Information


Prequest:
Midnight Sun
King of Fang and Claw
Note: Level 84 is needed to start this quest.

Given By: Pacal Redmask

Giver Location: The Zocalo
This is a side quest.

Goals:
Talk to Tezcat Threestar
Hand In: Tezcat Threestar

Reward:

55
4,080


Leads to:

Third Star on the Left

Quest Dialogue


This page is for recording a complete Quest Dialogue of all the conversation and story during a quest.
This includes NPC discussions, Narrator statements, and Creature speeches.


Documentation on how to edit this page can be found at Template:QuestInfobox/doc.

Hints, guides, and discussions of the Wiki content related to Across the Universe should be placed in the Wiki Page Discussion Forums.

Search for content related to Across the Universe in the Central Wiki Forums by clicking here.
